Name: Voxrush
About the game: Voxrush is a time survival FPS game with a full destructible voxel environment. Kill monsters, take points, upgrade stats and weapons, use skills and find a better way to survive as long as possible to become the best! Each enemy has a different features, so be carefull with them.
